div.p:
To proof. Botanical names checked.
Prof. Tates Flora not entered in Census
i.e. Tate (1880). as S.A.
The list, presumably written by Tate, has been annotated by M; his comments are on the right hand side of the page. Many names have been deleted from the list by M; these are listed separately here: 'Bassia Dallachyana [which M has marked with an exclamation point], Crotalaria linifolia and C. medicaginea, Neptunia gracilis, Acacia pyrifolia and A. dealbata; Grevillea agrifolia, Hakea chordophylla, Styphelia stricta, Cryptostylis longifolia, Stipa Tuckeri, Botrychium ternatum, Eremophila Behriana, Dichelachne (Stipa) sciurea and D. crinita, Erysimum lasiocarpum, Dysphania simulans, Kochia aphylla, Ptilotus Schwartzii, Gastrolobium elachistum; Eucalyptus cneorifolia, Wedelia platyglossa.
